	 <title>System.CompareText</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para>This operator performs a case insensitive compare of case sensitive
		  strings.</para> 
	 <example> 
		  <title>Example</title> 
		  <programlisting>select
	table { row { "Linter" Mixed, "LINTER" Caps } }
	add { CompareText(Mixed, Caps) Compare };</programlisting> 
		  <programlisting>Mixed  Caps   Compare 
------ ------ ------- 
Linter LINTER 0</programlisting> 
	 </example> 
